# KERNAL (kernelsx.ud3, CRC 7858d3d7) and the Swedish character generator
# (charswe.ud1, bee9b3fd — byte-identical to c64_se's charswe.u5). Both are
# carried by the split-set vip64.zip. Its BASIC (901226-01.ud4) and PLA
# (906114-01.ue4) are byte-identical in content to c64's members, located by
# CRC32 in the parent c64.zip and repacked under the board-position names vip64
# expects. The mixed-provenance c64gs / sx64 precedent. pal_sx replaces the iec8
# default with the built-in sx1541 drive — built-in hardware, never removed: no
# -iec8 override, the sx1541 device romset ships and the internal drive is
# present under the Swedish SX kernal's BASIC sign-on.
