# sx1541 (SX1541 disk drive) — a DEVICE romset, not a machine: the BUILT-IN
# drive of the SX-64 family (sx64/sx64p/vip64/tesa6240 at iec8, and TWICE on
# dx64 at iec8+iec9). Ground truth src/devices/bus/cbmiec/c1541.cpp,
# ROM_START( sx1541 ), device shortname "sx1541" — the zip name MAME's rompath
# lookup demands. Built-in hardware is never removed (D.'s ruling), so these
# machines carry no -iec8/-iec9 override and require this romset. The
# self-contained split-set zip is staged byte-for-byte (already TORRENTZIPPED);
# four members pinned. Default BIOS is r5 (ROM_SYSTEM_BIOS 0): 325302-01.uab4
# (always loaded) + "901229-05 ae.uab5" (r5) are the loaded pair; the jiffydos
# and flash alternates ride along for set-completeness. Member filenames carry
# spaces and must be preserved verbatim.
